'''John Jude Palencar''' is a worldly renowned illustrator, usually working on fantasy, science fiction and horror book covers. He did the cover art for ''[[Darth Bane: Path of Destruction]]'' and ''[[Darth Bane: Dynasty of Evil]]'', the first and third book in the [[Star Wars: Darth Bane Trilogy|''Darth Bane Trilogy'']].{{Mediacat|imagecat=images by John Jude Palencar}}

